              "display": "INVALID: isSubpotent=false, subpotentReason present. Core violation — subpotentReason must not appear when isSubpotent is false."
            },
            {
              "system": "http://example.org/test-case-tags",
              "code": "violation",
              "display": "imm-2: subpotentReason.exists() is true but isSubpotent = false"
